{"tid":2296061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為手機通話中爆炸 嚇傻怒控「才剛買2個月」","createTime":"2020-11-22T07:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T11:12:48.000Z","uid":8307,"like":198,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"6a38b6fa408cd86764d24e2cbfd202603e21b9ad","tid":2296061,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/yPwRXq9nSudvcRI88WFWXwAeMpc=/579x436/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/STQTKOKPUBFQPPLJOGSRIMDX6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyPwRXq9nSudvcRI88WFWXwAeMpc%3D%2F579x436%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSTQTKOKPUBFQPPLJOGSRIMDX6E.jpg&h=50341ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《太陽報》報導，25歲愛爾蘭女子肯尼(Aoife Kenny)說，她跟丈夫喬納森(Jonathan)打電話的時候，丈夫的手機突然爆炸了，「手機是8月19日買的，10月25日，我丈夫在工作，我打電話給他，經過一兩分鐘的交談，電話就壞了」，由於突然沒辦法聯繫到丈夫，讓她以為丈夫出事，「當他晚上7點下班回家，他說看看他的手機，才知道發生了什麼事」。<br />\n<br />\n全文；<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201121/R4F53KL3IVBBFE3PMZI3VQMSSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201121%2FR4F53KL3IVBBFE3PMZI3VQMSSU%2F&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=6b57c84b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201121%2FR4F53KL3IVBBFE3PMZI3VQMSSU%2F&h=7032587a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201121/R4F53KL3IVBBFE3PMZI3VQMSSU/</a>"},{"pid":"babb77b8fcd529f18a9d9f53ef81193a2c3a5670","tid":2296061,"uid":8307,"like":124,"dislike":1,"score":123,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:45:29.000Z","msg":"點解咁多鬼佬仲買華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a5b5c0cee0fdc054add421890a1ce91d9feed1","tid":2296061,"uid":22736,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:49:10.